00:14:53,100 --> 00:14:54,500
Hope there's no more war.

294
00:14:54,860 --> 00:14:55,420
Yeah,

295
00:14:55,860 --> 00:14:56,300
it's been hard

296
00:14:56,340 --> 00:14:57,700
to finally live in peaceful times.

297
00:14:57,700 --> 00:15:05,670
[Honglu Inn]

298
00:15:16,020 --> 00:15:17,540
You must be tired after a long journey.

299
00:15:17,780 --> 00:15:18,540
All your needs

300
00:15:18,780 --> 00:15:19,740
have been prepared.

301
00:15:20,140 --> 00:15:21,620
Please rest here for today.

302
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:24,100
[Consul of Honglu Inn]
You'll meet Her Majesty at Chen hour.

303
00:15:24,780 --> 00:15:25,420
Thank you for the arrangement.

304
00:15:35,060 --> 00:15:35,740
Prince of Chunyang knows

305
00:15:35,820 --> 00:15:36,780
you're arriving today,

306
00:15:36,940 --> 00:15:37,900
so he prepared some gifts

307
00:15:37,900 --> 00:15:38,500
for Your Highness.

308
00:15:38,620 --> 00:15:39,820
A pair of phoenix jade porcelain bowls,

309
00:15:39,980 --> 00:15:40,940
a flower glass vase,

310
00:15:41,180 --> 00:15:42,260
a jade mirror case with nine turtles,
and so on.

311
00:15:42,540 --> 00:15:43,460
Please accept them, Your Highness.

312
00:15:44,860 --> 00:15:45,740
Prince of Chunyang

313
00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:47,100
is very thoughtful.

314
00:15:55,300 --> 00:15:57,380
I heard Prince of Chunyang,
Wu Liangchen,

315
00:15:57,580 --> 00:15:58,420
is a handsome man.

316
00:15:58,780 --> 00:15:59,420
Your Highness.

317
00:16:01,180 --> 00:16:01,820
Your Highness?

318
00:16:04,780 --> 00:16:05,780
I've never seen

319
00:16:05,860 --> 00:16:06,940
such beautiful pomegranate flowers
in Shuodan.

320
00:16:07,780 --> 00:16:08,580
I've heard in Great Feng,

321
00:16:08,580 --> 00:16:10,180
pomegranates are given
as tokens of love.

322
00:16:10,540 --> 00:16:11,020
Haoji,

323
00:16:11,340 --> 00:16:12,100
where is General Wu staying?

324
00:16:12,380 --> 00:16:13,780
I'd like to pick a pomegranate flower
for him.

325
00:16:14,060 --> 00:16:14,740
Your Highness,

326
00:16:14,980 --> 00:16:16,100
why the rush?

327
00:16:16,300 --> 00:16:16,820
Why not

328
00:16:17,060 --> 00:16:17,980
burn incense, bathe,

329
00:16:18,180 --> 00:16:18,940
and turn in early?

330
00:16:19,540 --> 00:16:20,380
Tomorrow morning,

331
00:16:20,420 --> 00:16:21,820
you'll see your lover in the palace.

332
00:16:23,860 --> 00:16:24,380
You're right.

333
00:16:24,980 --> 00:16:26,020
I'll give it to him tomorrow.

334
00:16:39,950 --> 00:16:42,600
[Xu Qing, Chief Secretary
of the Ministry of Revenue]

335
00:16:43,220 --> 00:16:43,940
General Wu,

336
00:16:44,300 --> 00:16:46,420
since you've agreed
to meet me here for a drink,

337
00:16:46,900 --> 00:16:47,780
feel free

338
00:16:48,020 --> 00:16:49,140
to speak your mind.

339
00:16:52,940 --> 00:16:53,420
Sure.

340
00:16:53,940 --> 00:16:55,500
You haven't forgotten,
back in the second year of Shengxi,

341
00:16:55,700 --> 00:16:57,660
when you were the Granary Magistrate
of Jiahuai Granary in Bianzhou,

342
00:16:58,100 --> 00:16:58,900
you refused to transfer salt and grain

343
00:16:59,060 --> 00:17:00,740
to relieve the disaster
in Jinyuan, right?

344
00:17:05,620 --> 00:17:07,140
General Wu, let me tell you the truth.

345
00:17:07,660 --> 00:17:09,340
At that time,
there was a severe drought.

346
00:17:09,500 --> 00:17:11,380
Salt and grain were being diverted
for disaster relief.

347
00:17:11,660 --> 00:17:13,580
I refused the transfer
because we didn't have enough stock.

348
00:17:14,460 --> 00:17:16,540
It was a hard time not only
for Jiahuai Granary.

349
00:17:16,860 --> 00:17:17,580
Since it was hard,

350
00:17:17,980 --> 00:17:18,900
how do you explain that

351
00:17:19,140 --> 00:17:20,820
half a month before the transfer order,

352
00:17:21,460 --> 00:17:23,180
you secretly took a thousand dan of salt

353
00:17:23,700 --> 00:17:25,020
without reporting it
to the Ministry of Revenue?

354
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:37,070
[Jiahuai Granary, sealed]

355
00:17:42,940 --> 00:17:43,420
General Wu,

356
00:17:43,700 --> 00:17:45,020
you have no right
to inspect the granary records.

357
00:17:45,260 --> 00:17:46,580
Illegally taking the records
is a serious crime.

358
00:17:52,220 --> 00:17:52,940
Chief Secretary Xu,

359
00:17:53,380 --> 00:17:54,220
read it yourself.

360
00:18:09,300 --> 00:18:10,660
You asked

361
00:18:11,260 --> 00:18:12,380
to hear it.

362
00:18:13,260 --> 00:18:13,820
Alright.

363
00:18:16,260 --> 00:18:18,380
On the third day of the 12th month,
the Second Year of Shengxi,

364
00:18:18,820 --> 00:18:20,620
transfer 350 dan of salt

365
00:18:20,780 --> 00:18:21,940
as a gift to Prince of Wei, Li Xian,

366
00:18:22,140 --> 00:18:23,860
for his achievements
in pacifying the rebellion

367
00:18:24,660 --> 00:18:25,860
This is not reported
to the Ministry of Revenue.

368
00:18:26,020 --> 00:18:26,980
On the 26th day of the 12th month,

369
00:18:27,180 --> 00:18:28,260
transfer 500 dan of salt

370
00:18:28,380 --> 00:18:29,660
to be sold by Li Zongxu,

371
00:18:29,820 --> 00:18:31,340
with the proceeds going
to the national treasury.

372
00:18:31,740 --> 00:18:33,180
This is not reported
to the Ministry of Revenue.

373
00:18:33,540 --> 00:18:35,260
There were 150 dan...

374
00:18:40,460 --> 00:18:41,180
General Wu,

375
00:18:43,340 --> 00:18:44,940
I don't need to read the rest, right?

376
00:18:45,260 --> 00:18:47,100
It's all clearly written above

377
00:18:47,420 --> 00:18:49,260
and approved by the higher authorities.

378
00:18:49,980 --> 00:18:50,780
I understand.

379
00:18:51,140 --> 00:18:52,740
In the previous dynasty,
you tied these dirty accounts

380
00:18:52,900 --> 00:18:54,140
to the palace,

381
00:18:54,460 --> 00:18:55,380
making it impossible

382
00:18:55,620 --> 00:18:56,800
for anyone to investigate.

383
00:18:57,140 --> 00:18:57,940
This isn't something you,

384
00:18:58,060 --> 00:18:59,540
a mere chief secretary, could've dared

385
00:18:59,660 --> 00:19:00,660
to think or do.

386
00:19:01,700 --> 00:19:03,220
General Wu, would you consider

387
00:19:03,220 --> 00:19:05,220
the difficulties I faced?

388
00:19:05,780 --> 00:19:07,580
It wasn't that I didn't want
to transfer the salt.

389
00:19:07,820 --> 00:19:09,740
There was no salt left to transfer
in the Jiahuai Granary.

390
00:19:10,180 --> 00:19:11,180
If it's about requisitioning
military supplies,

391
00:19:11,340 --> 00:19:12,420
many places had more salt

392
00:19:12,540 --> 00:19:13,420
than Bianzhou had.

393
00:19:14,380 --> 00:19:15,660
At that time, how much official salt

394
00:19:16,300 --> 00:19:17,180
was Li Zongxu hoarding?

395
00:19:18,380 --> 00:19:19,180
I don't know.

396
00:19:20,420 --> 00:19:21,780
If you want to know,

397
00:19:22,900 --> 00:19:24,620
perhaps you should ask him in person.

398
00:19:37,340 --> 00:19:39,260
Master is already
waiting for you, Miss Ye.

399
00:19:39,540 --> 00:19:39,900
Please.

400
00:19:48,460 --> 00:19:48,860
General,

401
00:19:49,100 --> 00:19:49,820
should we still go?

402
00:19:51,020 --> 00:19:51,540
No.

403
00:19:52,340 --> 00:19:52,700
Let's go.

404
00:20:01,020 --> 00:20:01,540
Master,

405
00:20:01,780 --> 00:20:02,660
Miss Ye has arrived.

406
00:20:05,500 --> 00:20:06,060
Your Highness.

407
00:20:07,060 --> 00:20:07,740
Miss Ye,

408
00:20:08,340 --> 00:20:09,780
since your last visit,

409
00:20:10,420 --> 00:20:11,060
I haven't seen

410
00:20:11,220 --> 00:20:12,220
that creature again.

411
00:20:12,340 --> 00:20:13,180
I've used divination to foresee

412
00:20:13,740 --> 00:20:14,340
that tonight

413
00:20:14,580 --> 00:20:15,940
is the best opportunity

414
00:20:16,060 --> 00:20:17,020
to eliminate the evil.

415
00:20:17,460 --> 00:20:18,740
I need to set up a formation
at the house.

416
00:20:20,660 --> 00:20:21,460
Tonight?

417
00:20:22,420 --> 00:20:24,020
If we miss tonight,

418
00:20:24,420 --> 00:20:26,300
we'll have to wait at least two months.

419
00:20:27,420 --> 00:20:28,100
Your Highness,

420
00:20:28,420 --> 00:20:29,980
you don't want any more delays, do you?

421
00:20:31,980 --> 00:20:32,300
Alright.

422
00:20:33,340 --> 00:20:35,020
Then we'll do as you say.

423
00:20:52,900 --> 00:20:53,740
Sir,

424
00:20:54,420 --> 00:20:56,220
I'll set up the formation here shortly.

425
00:20:56,820 --> 00:20:57,780
Before dawn,

426
00:20:58,020 --> 00:20:59,500
no one is allowed near this place.

427
00:21:00,060 --> 00:21:00,740
Otherwise,

428
00:21:01,100 --> 00:21:02,660
the formation will be disrupted.

429
00:21:03,340 --> 00:21:03,820
Understood.

430
00:21:04,340 --> 00:21:05,180
I'll go give orders

431
00:21:05,300 --> 00:21:06,060
to the servants.

432
00:21:17,270 --> 00:21:21,150
[Langyang Mansion]

433
00:22:14,900 --> 00:22:15,780
You've never

434
00:22:16,260 --> 00:22:17,660
replied to my letters.

435
00:22:18,580 --> 00:22:19,900
Now, you ask me to come.

436
00:22:20,780 --> 00:22:22,100
Isn't it a bit insincere?

437
00:22:23,260 --> 00:22:25,740
You still know less about the capital.

438
00:22:26,020 --> 00:22:27,500
There are eyes everywhere here.

439
00:22:28,020 --> 00:22:29,300
If the letter falls
into the wrong hands,

440
00:22:29,420 --> 00:22:30,340
it'll be solid evidence.

441
00:22:30,900 --> 00:22:32,460
Face-to-face

442
00:22:32,700 --> 00:22:34,260
is the safest way to talk.

443
00:22:35,740 --> 00:22:37,500
So, are you willing to cooperate with us

444
00:22:38,020 --> 00:22:39,660
and sell salt to us

445
00:22:39,780 --> 00:22:40,580
at 30% below market price?

446
00:22:41,180 --> 00:22:43,220
The salt is negotiable,

447
00:22:44,660 --> 00:22:46,300
but about the prince consort...

448
00:22:47,660 --> 00:22:49,100
Feel free to name your price.

449
00:22:49,980 --> 00:22:51,420
You want us to choose

450
00:22:51,740 --> 00:22:53,220
someone from the Li family
as the prince consort?

451
00:22:53,500 --> 00:22:54,580
Quite the opposite.

452
00:22:54,900 --> 00:22:56,180
In Her Majesty's mind,

453
00:22:56,420 --> 00:22:58,820
our Li family's ties to the court

454
00:22:59,260 --> 00:23:00,780
are dangerous.

455
00:23:01,100 --> 00:23:02,580
If someone from the Li family
becomes the prince consort,

456
00:23:03,180 --> 00:23:04,260
and war breaks out again,

457
00:23:05,020 --> 00:23:07,020
can you control her?

458
00:23:09,340 --> 00:23:10,780
Turns out only your people

459
00:23:13,540 --> 00:23:15,900
can guess what your empress is thinking.

460
00:23:20,020 --> 00:23:21,660
I want to recommend someone.

461
00:23:23,660 --> 00:23:24,500
Wu Ankang.

462
00:23:25,420 --> 00:23:27,180
If Wu Ankang becomes the prince consort,

463
00:23:27,700 --> 00:23:28,260
not only can you

464
00:23:28,340 --> 00:23:29,780
take away a skilled general,

465
00:23:30,340 --> 00:23:32,500
but you can also use him as a hostage.

466
00:23:33,180 --> 00:23:33,820
Her Majesty

467
00:23:34,900 --> 00:23:36,700
will have to think twice
before taking action.

468
00:23:39,260 --> 00:23:40,300
You don't have

469
00:23:41,260 --> 00:23:42,660
to worry about this.

470
00:23:43,060 --> 00:23:44,100
Our princess

471
00:23:44,580 --> 00:23:46,700
already likes General Wu.

472
00:23:47,980 --> 00:23:48,780
Great.

473
00:23:49,580 --> 00:23:51,260
It seems we are

474
00:23:51,340 --> 00:23:52,500
natural friends.

475
00:23:54,500 --> 00:23:55,100
Since

476
00:23:55,940 --> 00:23:56,980
we're friends,

477
00:23:57,220 --> 00:23:58,820
let me remind you.

478
00:23:59,300 --> 00:24:01,260
The capital is full of danger.

479
00:24:02,260 --> 00:24:03,980
Never underestimate it.

480
00:24:05,740 --> 00:24:06,580
Danger?

481
00:24:07,980 --> 00:24:09,540
We're here for a marriage alliance.

482
00:24:10,180 --> 00:24:10,900
Is there anyone

483
00:24:11,340 --> 00:24:12,020
who dares

484
00:24:12,100 --> 00:24:13,540
to move against us?

485
00:24:13,940 --> 00:24:14,660
Now,

486
00:24:14,980 --> 00:24:16,260
many officials

487
00:24:16,660 --> 00:24:18,220
get their positions

488
00:24:18,300 --> 00:24:19,340
through their military achievements.

489
00:24:19,940 --> 00:24:21,100
They watched

490
00:24:21,260 --> 00:24:22,580
their brothers

491
00:24:22,740 --> 00:24:23,780
die on the battlefield,

492
00:24:23,940 --> 00:24:25,420
and held grudges.

493
00:24:25,660 --> 00:24:28,260
They might not be so eager
to turn hostility into friendship.

494
00:24:29,740 --> 00:24:31,580
So, keep your guard up.

495
00:24:48,220 --> 00:24:48,700
Master.

496
00:24:49,220 --> 00:24:50,540
Find a few death warriors,

497
00:24:50,940 --> 00:24:51,940
disguise them as Mang Gutter people,

498
00:24:52,380 --> 00:24:54,220
and get a skilled archer.

499
00:24:54,500 --> 00:24:56,740
During the banquet for the envoys,

500
00:24:56,980 --> 00:24:57,740
take action.

501
00:25:00,300 --> 00:25:01,980
If something happens to the envoy,

502
00:25:02,100 --> 00:25:04,060
Master, your business with them...

503
00:25:06,180 --> 00:25:08,180
As long as that arrow is shot,

504
00:25:10,580 --> 00:25:12,580
we can accuse the Mang Gutter people

505
00:25:12,700 --> 00:25:14,500
of trying to assassinate the envoy.

506
00:25:14,660 --> 00:25:15,780
If Mang Gutter gets involved,

507
00:25:16,180 --> 00:25:18,780
it'll point straight to Yuan Shaocheng.

508
00:25:21,140 --> 00:25:22,420
But Yuan Shaocheng...

509
00:25:35,580 --> 00:25:35,980
Master,

510
00:25:36,340 --> 00:25:37,060
there's nothing unusual.

511
00:25:40,700 --> 00:25:41,060
Let's go.

512
00:25:41,500 --> 00:25:42,780
Check on Miss Ye.

513
00:25:52,860 --> 00:25:53,460
Master,

514
00:25:54,180 --> 00:25:55,020
as you ordered,

515
00:25:55,180 --> 00:25:56,020
I've been watching all night.

516
00:25:56,220 --> 00:25:57,540
Miss Ye has been performing rituals

517
00:25:57,620 --> 00:25:58,460
and hasn't left.

518
00:26:00,460 --> 00:26:01,740
Keep a close watch.

519
00:26:01,940 --> 00:26:02,380
Yes.

520
00:26:10,220 --> 00:26:11,660
I've learned from Honglu Inn

521
00:26:12,260 --> 00:26:13,500
that Shuodan's envoy Haoji

522
00:26:14,020 --> 00:26:15,540
is planning to visit
Langyang Mansion tonight.

523
00:26:35,380 --> 00:26:36,780
Find a few death warriors,

524
00:26:37,020 --> 00:26:38,260
disguise them as Mang Gutter people,

525
00:26:38,580 --> 00:26:40,420
and get a skilled archer.

526
00:26:40,740 --> 00:26:42,940
During the banquet for the envoys,

527
00:26:43,300 --> 00:26:43,980
take action.

528
00:26:54,420 --> 00:26:55,500
Shuodan envoy

529
00:26:55,660 --> 00:26:56,820
Apuna Haoji

530
00:26:57,140 --> 00:26:59,060
presents Your Majesty
with a precious gift,

531
00:26:59,260 --> 00:27:00,020
the Dustless Pearl,

532
00:27:00,580 --> 00:27:02,380
along with 2,000 fine horses,

533
00:27:02,580 --> 00:27:03,620
5,000 cattle and sheep,

534
00:27:03,980 --> 00:27:05,540
in hopes of welcoming
the Great Feng's prince consort

535
00:27:05,660 --> 00:27:06,820
and establishing a marriage alliance

536
00:27:07,220 --> 00:27:08,900
to secure a century of peace

537
00:27:09,100 --> 00:27:10,380
and no more wars.

538
00:27:12,940 --> 00:27:15,660
Shuodan wishes to form a bond,

539
00:27:16,260 --> 00:27:18,580
and our court will respond
with great courtesy.

540
00:27:19,300 --> 00:27:21,980
The Ministry of Rites is ordered

541
00:27:22,180 --> 00:27:24,020
to prepare the envoy's banquet
in three days,

542
00:27:24,420 --> 00:27:26,260
to forge an everlasting peace.

543
00:27:27,620 --> 00:27:28,380
Your Majesty,

544
00:27:29,100 --> 00:27:30,900
I, Prince of Langyang, Li Zongxu

545
00:27:31,140 --> 00:27:33,180
am volunteering to organize the banquet.

546
00:27:33,460 --> 00:27:34,660
As a close relative,

547
00:27:34,900 --> 00:27:35,900
his son, Qianzhao,

548
00:27:35,980 --> 00:27:37,780
is also a candidate
for the prince consort.

549
00:27:37,900 --> 00:27:38,940
This is

550
00:27:39,140 --> 00:27:40,940
a good intention.

551
00:27:41,220 --> 00:27:42,140
The Prince of Langyang

552
00:27:42,340 --> 00:27:44,460
is willing to prepare
for the banquet in person.

553
00:27:44,820 --> 00:27:46,500
He will certainly not disappoint me.

554
00:27:47,060 --> 00:27:47,740
Permission granted.

555
00:27:48,780 --> 00:27:49,780
Thank you, Your Majesty.

556
00:27:50,660 --> 00:27:51,820
Further request, Your Majesty.

557
00:27:52,140 --> 00:27:53,260
Please approve

558
00:27:53,660 --> 00:27:55,660
General Wu Ankang as the prince consort,

559
00:27:56,100 --> 00:27:57,860
and send him to Shuodan
for the marriage alliance.

560
00:28:02,460 --> 00:28:05,140
Wu Ankang is a general of Great Feng.

561
00:28:05,300 --> 00:28:06,940
He has been stationed
on the borders for years.

562
00:28:07,300 --> 00:28:08,900
How can he become a prince consort?

563
00:28:12,780 --> 00:28:13,500
Since Great Feng

564
00:28:13,700 --> 00:28:15,780
is sincerely seeking peace with Shuodan,

565
00:28:16,260 --> 00:28:16,900
why does it need

566
00:28:17,260 --> 00:28:19,220
to keep a general guarding the border?

567
00:28:19,900 --> 00:28:21,220
You must be joking.

568
00:28:21,740 --> 00:28:24,140
A general guarding the border
is a military strategy.

569
00:28:24,300 --> 00:28:25,580
It's irrelated to the marriage alliance.

570
00:28:26,100 --> 00:28:26,500
May I ask,

571
00:28:26,940 --> 00:28:28,140
once the alliance is formed,

572
00:28:28,460 --> 00:28:30,300
can Shuodan's generals

573
00:28:30,420 --> 00:28:31,100
withdraw their forces

574
00:28:31,140 --> 00:28:32,900
to the north of Mang Mountain?

575
00:28:33,780 --> 00:28:35,100
